			<td class="print">
				Issue closed because new feature developped in v2.1.<br />
In a big database of 300 projects, with a small imported file (about 10 rows), the feature does work well even if not efficcient: more than 10 minutes are required for importing. But on the same 300 projects database, with a big imported file (more than 300 rows), the importation never ends: after 21 hours of execution, it hasn't ended.<br />
So this issue is marked as closed because the feature has been developed, but a new issue for this critical performance issue has been created for next version: <a href="view68c7.php?id=878" title="[closed] Import in mass mode with large files never ends" class="resolved">0000878</a> Import in mass mode with large files never ends .			</td>
